✨ Want to become a professional makeup artist? This is your chance! 💄

Our May-June PRO MAKEUP COURSE is back – and it’s bigger, bolder, and more transformative than ever! 🌟

📅 Dates: May 26th to June 8th 
🕚 Timings: 11 AM to 2 PM 
📍 Venue: AO Studio, Ludhiana 
📞 Register now: +91 9815923072

### 💼 What you’ll get:
- 6 AO Signature Looks – our most iconic and in-demand makeup styles.
- Theory + Social Media Class – learn to create, teach, and sell your artistry online 
- Business Class – everything you need to start your own freelance or salon career 
- Practice Sessions + Professional Portfolio Shoots – walk away with stunning photos of your work 
- Products for Practice (during the class)
- IAO Certification – globally recognized 
- Hairdo for models - during portfolio shoots 

Our past students are now working with top bridal clients, opening their own makeup studios and turning into beauty influencers! 💼💰

### 🎯 This is your time to level up.
Seats are extremely limited and usually fill up soon. Don’t miss the chance to learn from the best and start building the career you’ve always dreamt of.

📞 Call/WhatsApp +91 9815923072 to register NOW
📍 See you at AO Studio, Ludhiana!
